{"tid":2139824,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"42歲女子在網上商店Big Big Shop購得西洋菜進食後疑食物中毒","createTime":"2020-08-04T14:03:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T06:06:52.000Z","uid":53379,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"debdb801b8337734486af0ea31f2bbcc85fb3ae8","tid":2139824,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T14:03:40.000Z","msg":"衞生防護中心調查一宗懷疑食物中毒個案，涉事的42歲女子在網上商店Big Big Shop購得西洋菜，上月31日進食後出現喉嚨腫痛、腹痛、噁心及腹瀉等，本月1日求醫，現已痊癒。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心說，市民應留意含草酸鈣針晶體的蔬菜，誤食這類植物會刺傷和刺激皮膚及黏膜，如舌頭、口腔與咀唇麻痺和灼熱，進食混有草酸鈣針晶體的蔬菜亦可能引致食物中毒。<br />\n<br />\n中心呼籲市民切勿採食野生植物， 從可靠的供應商購買蔬菜，及取走混在食用蔬菜裏的其他植物，煮食前徹底洗淨。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/116440709_3702606296514066_9054628473071493220_o.png?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=74nTQjSsvKEAX_AZIOd&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=bf585bd00de0cd513896fa5789bb06ff&amp;oe=5F4F00B3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F116440709_3702606296514066_9054628473071493220_o.png%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3D74nTQjSsvKEAX_AZIOd%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3Dbf585bd00de0cd513896fa5789bb06ff%26oe%3D5F4F00B3&h=ab7f024c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/photos/a.723529797755079/3702606289847400/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fphotos%2Fa.723529797755079%2F3702606289847400%2F&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4YdxZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=401a9b9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/photos/a.723529797755079/3702606289847400/</a>"},{"pid":"dd9f02d51177db6b31aba286e2604b5b52877b05","tid":2139824,"uid":199893,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T14:05:13.000Z","msg":"恭喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" cl